=== ANCIENT_MURAL ===
# id: 12
# title: The Ancient Mural
# chinese_title: 古壁画
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

The corridor walls are covered in murals depicting beings of light traveling between worlds. The artwork predates any known civilization by millennia. Certain panels seem to glow faintly when you approach, responding to your presence.

* [Study the beings depicted in the mural]
  ~ gain_radical("人")
  "人" (rén) — person, human, being
* [Touch the glowing panels]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "古" (gǔ) — ancient, old
* [Take scrapings for analysis]
  ~ gain_gold(20)
  "色" (sè) — color
